From 7f1e815a6068b2bb1d5279ccff783759eda3794c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 03:35:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Modernize portfolio navigation, animations, and UX

- Replace opaque nav state management with CSS class-based approach
  (.scrolled on nav-bar, .open on head-nav overlay) for cleaner transitions
- Rewrite index page as full-screen hero with glass pill nav buttons,
  dark overlay for readability, and staggered entrance animations
- Add animated underline indicator on active/hovered nav links
- Slim hamburger bars with smoother X transform animation
- Mobile overlay nav slides in with staggered link fade-up on open
- Content areas fade up on page load via CSS keyframe animation
- Profile image gets rounded corners, shadow, and lift-on-hover effect
- Experience page: sticky resume sidebar and better content grid
- Projects page: two-column layout for image-bearing projects,
  flex image galleries with hover lift, section separators
- Footer links get pill hover highlight and lift animation
- CSS custom properties for consistent accent color and easing
- Improve typography: line-height, letter-spacing, font-weight hierarchy
- Add DOCTYPE and lang="en" to all HTML pages

https://claude.ai/code/session_01J9X5A6EDvxKTh6BH7YhZjS
